patthana16.27:1.1_0: Vipākaṁ hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca navipāko nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Vipākaṁ
patthana16.27:1.1_1: hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca navipākadhammadhammo nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Vipākaṁ
patthana16.27:1.1_2: hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nanevavipākanavipākadhammadhammo nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.27:1.1_3: Vipākaṁ hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca navipākadhammadhammo nahetu ca nanevavipākanavipākadhammadhammo
patthana16.27:1.1_4: nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. Vipākaṁ hetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca navipāko nahetu
patthana16.27:1.1_5: ca navipākadhammadhammo nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā … pañca.

patthana16.27:2.1_6: nahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā … pañca.

patthana16.27:4.1: Hetuyā terasa, ārammaṇe nava …pe… aññamaññe ekādasa …pe… āsevane cha …pe… vipāke pañca …pe… avigate terasa.
patthana16.27:5.1_0: Vipākaṁ nahetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca navipākadhammadhammo nanahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.

patthana16.27:5.1_2: uppajjati hetupaccayā. Vipākaṁ nahetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca navipākadhammadhammo nanahetu
patthana16.27:5.1_3: ca nanevavipākanavipākadhammadhammo nanahetu ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā … tīṇi.

patthana16.27:8.1: Vipākaṁ nahetuñca nevavipākanavipākadhammadhammaṁ nahetuñca dhammaṁ paṭicca navipākadhammadhammo nanahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
